  "text": "Tesseract is an OCR engine designed at Hewlett-Packard (HP) between 1984 and 1994. Since late 2005, it has been maintained by Google and released as open source OCR software. However, Arabic support has only been added recently [CITATION_1] . Tesseract is the only Arabic OCR software that is freely available. It supports multi-font types, and multi-size and multi-resolution images.",
